reviews.ReviewText: This cereal was delicious I am a 55 year old man and I bought these because they said they had a lot of fiber for my little tummy and it helped me learn to count and this wasn’t even the only cereal I got the froot loops, trix, fruity pebbles, and fruity pebbles with marshmallows were extra fruity I loved them. The coco puffs were so coco when they made my milk chocolate I got so excited. The dunkaroos were so good I got 2 boxes they were extra dunky. The apple jacks might have been my favorite they were so good they were extra apple flavored. The captain crunch was so crunch I loved it. The rice crispeses were so good I was and when I poured the milk in i got so excited it was making a sound like snap crackle pop. The corn pops they were the first one i had and they were so good. Frosted Flakes and cookie crisp was so good I loved them the the cookies were so good in the cookie crisp. The lucky charms are no magic treasures but they were magically delicious and they were even better on saint patricks day i just wish i bought the ones that turn the milk green. The oreos were so good. I can’t forget about the cinnamon roll frosted mini wheats. The only problem is that I just ate 17 boxes of cereal in 3 weeks.
